  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="NA260-kiḷavi">uṭaṉ maṟutta talaimakaḷ colliyatu.</p>
        <p xml:lang="en">What is said by HER who refused [going away] together.
            G1+2: This is what is said by HIM who refused going away together.</p>
        </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="NA260">
<l>            kaḻaṉi mēynta karuntā ḷerumai</l>
<l>            paḻaṉat tāmaraip paṉimalar muṇaiit</l>
<l>            taṇṭucēr maḷḷari ṉiyali yayalatu</l>
<l>            kuṉṟucēr veṇmaṇaṟ ṟuñcu mūra</l>
<l>            veyyai pōla muyaṅkuti muṉaiyeḻat </l>
<l>            tevvart tēytta cevvēl vayavaṉ</l>
<l>            malipuṉal vāyi liruppai yaṉṉaveṉ</l>
<l>            ṉolipal kūnta ṉalampeṟap puṉainta</l>
<l>            mukaiyaviḻ kōtai vāṭṭiya</l>
<l>            pakaivaṉ maṉyāṉ maṟantamai kalaṉē.</l>
            </lg>
        <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O man from a village,</l>
<l rend="indent3">where the black-legged buffalo cow that grazed the fields,</l>
<l rend="indent3">disliking the dewy blossom of the lotus in the tank</l>
<l rend="indent3">moves forward as a warrior with [his] club</l>
<l rend="indent3">[and] sleeps in the white sand joining to the neary hills,</l>
<l>you embrace [me] as if you were keen.</l>
<l>He [is] an enemy indeed, who made the garland</l>
<l rend="indent">with opening buds fade that decorated for obtaining goodness</l>
<l rend="indent">my flourishing many tresses, as wealthy(?) Puṉalvāyil Iruppai<note place="foot"><term xml:lang="ta">mali puṉal vāyil iruppai</term>: here T.V.G. wants to read one long name, but it seems also possible to take the first part attributive: "Iruppai with abounding flood up to [its] doors". <term xml:lang="ta">Iruppai</term> is described as <term xml:lang="ta">Virāṉ</term>’s place in NA 350.4 and AiN 58.</note>,</l>
<l rend="indent2">[belonging to] the strong one with straight spear who reduced</l>
<l rend="indent2">[his] foes, when the front rose.</l>
<l rend="indent4">I have not completely forgotten.</l>
        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
